Prophet.Commentary: Come and see the works of God: He is terrible in His doing toward the children of men (Psalms 66:5). Yet, behold, therein shall be left a remnant that shall be brought forth, both sons and daughters: behold, they shall come forth unto you, and you shall see their way and their doings: and you shall be comforted concerning the evil that I have brought upon Jerusalem, even concerning all that I have brought upon it (Ezekiel 14:22). They shall comfort you, when you see their ways and their doings: and you shall know that I have not done without cause all that I have done in it, said the Lord GOD (Ezekiel 14:23).
